      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "HASH VAULT (image-only API) — caching the Gemini Style Transfer node\n\nStyle Transfer takes (image, style, intensity, ...) and emits a styled image — no prompt STRING anywhere. v1.2.0 of API-Optimizer made Hash Vault's payload_string optional and added any_input_2/3/4, so we can hash purely on image + converted-widget values.\n\nWIRING\nLoadImage routes to BOTH Style Transfer.image AND Hash Vault.any_input.\nThe two StringConstantMultiline nodes hold the style and intensity values; each routes to BOTH the corresponding Style Transfer input (the widgets are converted to inputs) AND Hash Vault.any_input_2 / any_input_3.\n\nResult: same image + same style + same intensity → cache hit → no API call. Change any of the three → new hash → API runs once, then cached.\n\nNOT CACHED: the Style Transfer node still has its own model / seed / aspect_ratio / resolution / direction widgets that DON'T factor into the hash here. If you change those and want a fresh render, clear the matching .pt file in output/hash_vault/ first. Or wire those through additional any_input slots if you have them free.\n\nREQUIRES\nComfyUI-API-Optimizer v1.2.0+, ComfyUI-Gemini-Direct, ComfyUI-KJNodes (StringConstantMultiline). Any STRING primitive substitutes for KJNodes if you don't have it."
      ]
    },
